high_descs: Turn around and then right and go to the stove.
Turn around and go to the fridge on your left.
Put the pan in the fridge.
Pick up an egg from the bottom shelf.
Put the egg on the pan.
anns.task_desc: Put an egg in a pan in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn around and begin walking across the room, then hang a right and walk up to the stove.
Pick up the frying pan that is on the front left burner of the stove.
Turn around and begin walking across the room, then turn left and walk up to the fridge.
Open the lower compartment of the fridge and place the frying pan inside on the top shelf.
Pick up the egg that is on the lower shelf in the fridge.
Place the egg on the frying pan inside the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Place an egg on a frying pan inside a fridge.

high_descs: Walk across the room to the stove.
Pick up the pan on the left front burner of the stove.
Put the pan in to the fridge.
Take the egg out of the fridge.
Put the egg in the pan.
anns.task_desc: Put a pan with an egg in it into the fridge.
